00:21:15.280 --> 00:21:17.000
Rizzo's pregnant.

254
00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:24.400
Rizzo's got a bun in the oven.

255
00:21:35.280 --> 00:21:37.000
Rizzo's knocked up.

256
00:21:41.080 --> 00:21:43.000
Rizzo. I hear you're knocked up.

257
00:21:43.160 --> 00:21:46.200
You do?
Boy. good news really travels fast.

258
00:21:47.080 --> 00:21:49.000
Why didn't you tell me about it?

259
00:21:49.680 --> 00:21:51.200
What's it to you?

260
00:21:51.360 --> 00:21:54.320
- I might be able to do something.
- You did enough.

261
00:21:56.080 --> 00:21:59.000
I don't run away from my mistakes.

262
00:21:59.160 --> 00:22:03.040
Don't worry about it. Kenickie.
It was somebody else's mistake.

263
00:22:08.480 --> 00:22:10.200
Thanks a lot. kid.

264
00:22:11.160 --> 00:22:12.800
Any time.

265
00:22:19.200 --> 00:22:20.600
Are you getting a cold?

266
00:22:20.760 --> 00:22:25.200
No. It's probably
a little drive-in dust. that's all.

267
00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:41.400
Danny. what are you doing?

268
00:22:41.560 --> 00:22:43.600
Don't worry. nobody's watching.

269
00:22:43.760 --> 00:22:47.000
- Get off me.
- Sandy. what's the matter with you?

270
00:22:47.960 --> 00:22:50.600
I thought I meant something to you.

271
00:22:50.760 --> 00:22:55.680
Think I'm gonna stay with you in this
sin-wagon? Take this piece of tin!

272
00:22:56.680 --> 00:22:59.040
Sandy. you can't walk out
of a drive-in!

273
00:23:08.880 --> 00:23:11.200
Stranded at the drive-in

274
00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:15.600
Branded a fool

275
00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:18.760
What will they say

276
00:23:20.080 --> 00:23:22.800
Monday at school?

277
00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:32.000
Sandy

278
00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:34.120
Can't you see

279
00:23:34.280 --> 00:23:36.840
I'm in misery?

280
00:23:38.280 --> 00:23:40.200
We made a start

281
00:23:40.360 --> 00:23:42.400
Now we're apart

282
00:23:42.560 --> 00:23:45.600
There's nothing left for me

283
00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:48.800
Love has flown

284
00:23:48.960 --> 00:23:50.720
All alone

285
00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:54.800
I sit and wonder why

286
00:23:54.960 --> 00:23:58.200
Why you left me

287
00:23:59.280 --> 00:24:00.920
Oh. Sandy

288
00:24:02.360 --> 00:24:04.600
Oh. Sandy

289
00:24:04.760 --> 00:24:06.720
Maybe

290
00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:08.520
Someday

291
00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:11.640
When high school is done

292
00:24:13.120 --> 00:24:16.400
Somehow. some way

293
00:24:17.160 --> 00:24:20.280
Our two worlds will be one

294
00:24:21.480 --> 00:24:23.320
In heaven

295
00:24:23.480 --> 00:24:25.400
Forever

296
00:24:25.560 --> 00:24:28.800
And ever we will be

297
00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:33.000
Please. say you'll stay

298
00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:36.200
Oh. Sandy

299
00:24:39.480 --> 00:24:41.920
Sandy. my darling.

300
00:24:42.080 --> 00:24:44.000
you hurt me real bad.

301
00:24:45.080 --> 00:24:47.000
You know it's true.

302
00:24:47.760 --> 00:24:50.600
But. baby. you gotta believe me
when I say...

303
00:24:52.360 --> 00:24:54.280
