304
00:24:55.160 --> 00:24:57.120
Love has flown

305
00:24:57.280 --> 00:24:59.000
All alone

306
00:24:59.160 --> 00:25:03.000
I sit. I wonder why

307
00:25:03.160 --> 00:25:06.760
Why you left me

308
00:25:07.680 --> 00:25:10.000
Oh. Sandy

309
00:25:22.680 --> 00:25:26.200
Why?

310
00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:29.600
Oh. Sandy!

311
00:25:34.160 --> 00:25:36.000
Head it out. Come on. guys.

312
00:25:42.880 --> 00:25:44.880
Well. the crate shaped up.

313
00:25:45.040 --> 00:25:48.200
