- Just wait till Thunder Road.

315
00:25:51.960 --> 00:25:54.400
Right. You could still
change your mind.

316
00:25:54.560 --> 00:25:58.040
- The flag is in three hours.
- And Greased Lightning strikes.

317
00:25:58.200 --> 00:26:00.880
- You coming?
- My boys won't let me down.

318
00:26:01.040 --> 00:26:02.800
and I won't let them down.

319
00:26:05.360 --> 00:26:07.400
I wanna talk to you.

320
00:26:09.560 --> 00:26:12.840
Those guys at Thunder Road
don't fool around. you know.

321
00:26:14.280 --> 00:26:15.760
You want me to punk out?

322
00:26:16.280 --> 00:26:19.000
No. I'm not saying punking out.
I'm just...

323
00:26:20.280 --> 00:26:22.200
You know what I mean.

324
00:26:25.760 --> 00:26:27.800
We been friends a long time. right?

325
00:26:31.080 --> 00:26:33.720
You remember the drive-in
the other night?

326
00:26:33.880 --> 00:26:37.200
The movie with the duel.
the guy's best friend went with him

327
00:26:37.360 --> 00:26:39.360
as his lieutenant. his second?

328
00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:41.240
Yeah. So?

329
00:26:43.280 --> 00:26:47.640
Well. I thought that you could
maybe be my second at Thunder Road.

330
00:26:48.280 --> 00:26:51.000
What. you want me
to drive with you or what?

331
00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:04.600
Listen. I'll pick you up at three.
alright?

332
00:27:05.680 --> 00:27:09.000
Open up the door.
What are you sitting around for?

333
00:27:09.160 --> 00:27:12.000
Take the can off
the front of the car. you putz.

334
00:27:18.280 --> 00:27:20.840
Hello. Rizz.
Are you going to Thunder Road?

335
00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:22.200
Not a chance.

336
00:27:22.360 --> 00:27:24.400
I have to go.
I have to talk to Danny.

337
00:27:24.560 --> 00:27:27.720
Without wheels and a motor.
he won't know you're alive.

338
00:27:27.880 --> 00:27:31.400
We haven't been friends.
but if there's anything I can do...

339
00:27:31.560 --> 00:27:35.400
I can take care of myself.
And anybody else who comes along.

340
00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:39.520
You think I don't know
what people are saying about me?

341
00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:45.960
Thanks.

342
00:27:56.080 --> 00:27:58.640
That's the one
I was telling you about.

343
00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:03.600
There are worse things I could do

344
00:28:04.480 --> 00:28:07.800
Than go with a boy or two

345
00:28:09.080 --> 00:28:11.120
Even though the neighbourhood

346
00:28:11.280 --> 00:28:14.280
Thinks I'm trashy and no good

347
00:28:15.080 --> 00:28:18.000
