397
00:32:41.480 --> 00:32:43.560
The rules are. there ain't no rules.

398
00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:46.440
To the second bridge and back.
First one back wins.

399
00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:49.800
Haul ass. kid.

400
00:33:08.680 --> 00:33:10.800
You ain't gonna see me
